description: Concrete is produced in Ready mix plants facilities, where the mixing of constituent material takes place in central mixer and discharged to agitator trucks and transported to final destination. Concrete is a mixture of Portland cement, natural gravel/crushed rock, natural/rock crushed sand and potable quality water, in addition to admixtures, Ground granulated Slag, fly ash or silica fume. Transgulf Readymix concrete provides many types of concrete mixtures to be used in different applications, which meet the needs of the projects requirements and performance.
